data: We have added a new builds page which provides a cleaner top down view of each characters most popular builds for each patch. The data for the current patch will be updated periodically as the leaderboard gets new submissions. Currently the top builds, weapons, tomes and items are listed but this may be expanded in the future. Thanks for the support!

Country filters have arrived. This has been one of our most requested features. Countries can be added or excluded in the same way as the other filters. In addition you can now also perform player instant search to find players across the entire leaderboard. In a previous hotfix we also added a "Sort By Rarity" button for run items. More updates coming soon! Thanks for all the support and keep the feature requests coming.

This patch added the much requested item filter. You all will probably get the most utility out of this by excluding items. A runs items are also now sorted by rarity. The weapon, tome and item tooltips have also been slightly restyled so they don't overlap their icons anymore. Thanks for all the support and keep the feature requests coming!
Run items now sorted by rarity
Weapon, Tome, Item tooltip styling fixed

In this patch we added the ability to exclude characters, weapons or tomes from the filters. We also modified it so you can select more of each of these filter types. This changelog was also added to help relay updates for the leaderboard better. Some optimizations where also added to improve the rendering speed of the leaderboard now that we have a constant flow of submissions.
You can now see all of your submitted runs under your profile, or by clicking the notification icon at the top. Pending, Rejected and Approved submissions will be shown.
Your runs are now highlighted green on the leaderboard
Rules and FAQ to submission flow.
Add a clear button to clear all filters.
